General.Name: Landsea Homes Corp
General.Description: Landsea Homes Corporation engages in the design, construction, marketing, and sale of suburban and urban single-family detached and attached homes in Arizona, California, Colorado, Florida, Texas, and Metro New York. The company develops homes and communities; and builds suburban, single-family detached and attached homes, mid-and high-rise properties, and master-planned communities. The company was incorporated in 2013 and is based in Dallas, Texas.
